results.title: Live Laugh Love Embroidered Multi Color Side Striped Tea Towel
results.description:
100% off-white Cotton tea towel with hanging loop.  Towel measures approx. 26 Inches Long by 17 Inches wide.  Towel blank manufactured in India and has a 1/2 inch hem on all sides with the towel stripes down the sides.  Embroidery design in polyester machine embroidery thread. 

This towel with its embroidered design is individually crafted in my home studio and not mass produced.   

Note:  In the process of stitching out the embroidery, a paper-like stabilizer is used on the underside of the design which is then carefully torn off when the design is complete.  Some fragments of the stabilizer may still be left in the small areas of the design (on the backside of the towel) until it is washed once or twice and then these fragments will disappear.  If you happen to come across any blue lines/spots on the towel, just squirt with water and they will also disappear.  They were left by my placement lines for the design.  I may have overlooked a spot or two with my water spray bottle after the towel was completed.

The towel may have a few small imperfections in the cotton weave called slubs which is normal in the manufacturing process and not a defect of the towel.  

This listing is for the towel seen in the primary listing photo.  Other similar designs may be shown in last photos and may be still available for purchase in a separate listing.  Convo if you have any questions before purchasing.

Item weighs approx. 4 ounces with packaging.  Shipping cost includes insurance and tracking.

We all hate overpaying for shipping and my listed shipping costs are best estimates for the individual item.  If you wish to purchase more than one item at one time, I can combine them in a special reserved listing for you and recalculate the weight and save you excess shipping/insurance/handling fees. I can also combine items from both of my stores into one purchase.  Please Convo before you make your purchases.
